{"tid":2330479,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王宗堯被控暴動罪今提堂：希望大家繼續關注12人","createTime":"2020-12-18T05:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T05:35:31.000Z","uid":271829,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f1b52440bda944d58ae1c509cba45dfe67de769b","tid":2330479,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:10:02.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n王宗堯今早10時50分抵達，見他戴上黃色口罩、身穿早前訂購印有「Uncovering The Truth, Confronting Injustice（用真相對抗不義）」的《蘋果》白色T恤，配上西裝褸、牛仔褲。他禮貌地應記者要求停步拍照，問及他心情如何？王宗堯說：「暫時係平常心，希望大家繼續關注12人及其他人士被捕嘅消息。」<br />\n王宗堯指這幾天很忙很累，所以昨晚能入睡，他續道：「有好多朋友聯絡我，見咗好多人，做咗好多嘢，（呢幾日）好充實，亦都希望自己今次呢個經驗，可以將呢件事做好佢，希望其他人有需要嘅朋友都可以得到一啲幫助。好！唔該晒。」之後步入法院，早上11時開庭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LYMC5AaVA_IR9QwtnNltPz_FAuQ=/711x516/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GB3XLVUU65GA3JP7IHSTMONL2M.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLYMC5AaVA_IR9QwtnNltPz_FAuQ%3D%2F711x516%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGB3XLVUU65GA3JP7IHSTMONL2M.JPG&h=c54bd3ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王宗堯前日獲得公民黨「飛機師」譚文豪邀請，以5位數字酬勞在譚文豪位於旺角新開的茶餐廳「一日三餐」擔任一日店長。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ei1wTddvFiDDP0Pi3Qvun9jgfG0=/713x459/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2CPGH5PG4FESZP4MOHIGCXV52Y.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fei1wTddvFiDDP0Pi3Qvun9jgfG0%3D%2F713x459%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2CPGH5PG4FESZP4MOHIGCXV52Y.JPG&h=0849aedf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《蘋果》「懲罰」王宗堯主持新節目《王探黃》，由他出動帶大家走勻全港黃店，昨日首站到《蘋果》踩場。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201218/EBTYGFV4MJFEXHG2JUNPHZHP2E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201218%2FEBTYGFV4MJFEXHG2JUNPHZHP2E%2F&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrZBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=6e8afb0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201218%2FEBTYGFV4MJFEXHG2JUNPHZHP2E%2F&h=c62fb535\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201218/EBTYGFV4MJFEXHG2JUNPHZHP2E/</a>"},{"pid":"07d9ce95734319e5bb1d78f89a3bc63fe2934343","tid":2330479,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:12:38.000Z","msg":"食少啲lady m 同大渣狗儲錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516771a1bb81a894685fd50a93b42ca14c004d94","tid":2330479,"uid":34811,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:23:55.000Z","msg":"人地俾人告暴動，食乜關隻南亞狗撚事咩？<br />\n想叫人食告暴動手足嘅龍門就過返飲食台la"},{"pid":"4849dd279da51bcb35a4f0295c93b16e0d7e946c","tid":2330479,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}